---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' });
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="RecastCalc privacy policy. We do not collect personal data, do not sell data, and do not require accounts."
>
  <article class="max-w-prose mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6 py-16 prose-recast">
    <h1 class="text-display-1 font-display font-semibold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-ink-500 mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>Calculator inputs (loan balance, rate, term, lump sum, etc.) never leave your browser.</strong>
      Calculations happen entirely client-side. We have no servers that store or process your loan data.
    </p>
    <p>
      We collect anonymous aggregate analytics (page views, country, referrer, device type) via a
      privacy-focused analytics tool. No personally identifiable information, no cross-site tracking,
      no behavioral profiling.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies and tracking</h2>
    <p>
      We use:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> for display ads. AdSense may set cookies to serve relevant ads. You can opt out at <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Google Ads Settings</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Affiliate tracking links</strong> to LendingTree, Credible, and similar lender comparison platforms. Clicking these may set cookies on the destination site (governed by that site's privacy policy, not ours).</li>
      <li><strong>No first-party tracking cookies.</strong> No remarketing pixels. No social media trackers.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Information we share</h2>
    <p>
      We do not sell, rent, or share user data. We have no email list. We have no user accounts.
      We have no CRM. We have no data to share even if we wanted to.
    </p>
    <p>
      Third-party services we use (AdSense, affiliate networks, hosting) have their own privacy
      policies governing data collected through their integrations.
    </p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>
      Because we don't collect personal data, there's nothing to request, correct, or delete from
      us. To control AdSense personalization, use <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Google Ads Settings</a>.
      To clear all third-party cookies, use your browser's privacy settings.
    </p>

    <h2>Children</h2>
    <p>
      RecastCalc is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from
      children.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy: <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
